New Issue Checklist
- [ ] Checked that the issue has not already been reported.
- [ ] Checked that the issue has not already been fixed in the latest code (a.k.a. master).
- [ ] Issue description of problem is clear, concise and precise.
- [ ] Issue has a a descriptive title and a summary in grammatically correct, complete sentences.
- [ ] Includes the version of ember-bootstrap-controls that you are using.
- [ ] Includes any relevant code to the issue summary.

Is this a bug or a feature request?

For bugs...
Is the problem be recreated? If so how?

For features...
Why is this feature important?
